{"tid":2130920,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"醫學交流成諜戰大漏洞","createTime":"2020-07-29T13:11:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T13:43:07.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6bb01bf62c653cabbfdfd0b8bc2f69d1a1e15f87","tid":2130920,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:11:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200729/YCSKAM6YOREQ43XU5NPPWRKDWI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200729%2FYCSKAM6YOREQ43XU5NPPWRKDWI%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6T4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=8bb95d38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200729%2FYCSKAM6YOREQ43XU5NPPWRKDWI%2F&h=84bffa48\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200729/YCSKAM6YOREQ43XU5NPPWRKDWI/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n醫學交流成諜戰大漏洞<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/UJkoxycPUyEfREXE816Jl0zbE_M=/640x409/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/GNYTJUUWGRZE3FVEOCUABFNYAE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FUJkoxycPUyEfREXE816Jl0zbE_M%3D%2F640x409%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FGNYTJUUWGRZE3FVEOCUABFNYAE.jpg&h=5527674e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李健健<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】擁解放軍背景的中國學者唐娟能到美國加州大學交流，有軍醫背景的美國專家研判，這可能與戴維斯分校內與中國有密切互動的學者有關，他擔心醫學交流或成為最無抵抗力的諜報漏洞。而近日被起訴簽證欺詐的四名學者中，三名與醫學研究相關，另一名從事人工智能科技研究。<br />\n<br />\n曾服務於美國軍醫傳染病研究所的塞林（Dr. Lawrence Sellin）上周六表示，唐娟能到加州大學戴維斯分校擔任訪問學者，可能與該校醫學院教授李健健（Jian-Jian Li）有關。李於1984年取得中國西安的空軍軍醫大學學位，目前是戴。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被起訴3人與醫研有關<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：美領事告別成都 「新方法建兩國友誼」<br />\n<br />\n值得注意，近期四名被起訴的中國學者中，有三人與醫學研究相關。包括FBI上月公佈具有解放軍背景的男子王新（Wang Xin）。。。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"1b9b660af7595c72fe4251f27dd6c3c4a042bb3a","tid":2130920,"uid":337525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T13:43:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTPwyvF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTPwyvF.jpg&h=06d56823&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}